111
00:07:45,390 --> 00:07:49,570
I deserve to be happy. I worked really hard for this.

112
00:07:49,570 --> 00:07:52,410
I've been doing so many assignments, too.

113
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:55,390
Is that why you've been down lately?

114
00:07:56,750 --> 00:08:00,240
Well... that's...

115
