116
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:14,500
Did I startle you the other day, Ida?

117
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,240
What?

118
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:21,890
When we were eating on the stairs, I suddenly touched your hand.

119
00:08:22,770 --> 00:08:24,750
I won't do it again.

120
00:08:25,380 --> 00:08:29,640
