151
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:48,370
So that means... that means Aoki is...

152
00:10:49,110 --> 00:10:52,590
Come to think of it, I feel like he looks up to me.

153
00:10:52,590 --> 00:10:56,250
Look, Mr. Okano! Ta-da!

154
00:10:57,690 --> 00:11:00,020
Did I startle you that bad?

155
00:11:01,700 --> 00:11:03,800
That's amazing! Full marks.

156
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:08,300
- Yes! Mr. Okano, do you remember?
- Remember what?

157
00:11:08,300 --> 00:11:12,770
You said, if I got 100 points on a quiz, you'd treat me to ramen.

158
00:11:15,060 --> 00:11:16,890
