159
00:11:16,890 --> 00:11:21,390
What? Why? I was looking forward to it.

160
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:24,540
- Treat me. Treat me.
- I'm not interested in you in that way.

161
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:27,990
Oops, it slipped out.

162
00:11:31,140 --> 00:11:34,880
Hey, listen...

163
00:11:35,550 --> 00:11:40,090
I saw you yesterday on the overpass.

164
00:11:42,110 --> 00:11:45,480
I didn't know

165
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:49,820
you swing that way, so...

166
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:53,530
I'm sorry, but I can't keep my promise.

167
00:11:53,530 --> 00:11:56,630
I won't tell anyone, of course.

168
00:11:58,830 --> 00:12:00,240
Okay.

169
00:12:01,060 --> 00:12:05,270
Thank you, Mr. Okano. Sorry for not telling you.

170
00:12:05,270 --> 00:12:09,250
No, it's my fault. Forgive me.

171
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,520
Sure.

172
00:12:15,850 --> 00:12:20,490
There is no surprise there. It's normal for people to react that way.

173
00:12:21,850 --> 00:12:28,650
So... why are we helping Aoki with his class chores?

174
00:12:28,650 --> 00:12:32,800
Aoki, did something happen?

175
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:34,350
