235
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:02,540
Sorry! Take care of the rest, okay?

236
00:16:02,540 --> 00:16:04,070
Okay.

237
00:16:07,550 --> 00:16:09,480
Are you in a hurry, Kosuke?

238
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:12,820
Yes. I made a promise to Aoki.

239
00:16:16,930 --> 00:16:20,740
Leave it to me. I'll take care of the rest for you.

240
00:16:20,740 --> 00:16:22,000
