241
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:25,950
Don't worry. Hey, don't leave him waiting.

242
00:16:27,550 --> 00:16:31,320
Sorry. Well... thank you.

243
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:32,760
Sure.

244
00:16:35,470 --> 00:16:39,790
Sorry, I'm running a little late. I'll meet you at the restaurant.

245
00:16:39,790 --> 00:16:43,380
