246
00:16:43,380 --> 00:16:46,640
- Excuse me, do you have a minute?
- Yes?

247
00:16:46,640 --> 00:16:50,130
I'm trying to find my way to this hotel.

248
00:16:52,410 --> 00:16:54,160
