Mr. Okano?

256
00:17:12,490 --> 00:17:14,880
Don't just stand there. Come with me.

257
00:17:20,230 --> 00:17:23,500
You need to value your body more.

258
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:26,500
Good night.

259
00:17:26,500 --> 00:17:30,590
What are you saying? I was just helping him find his way.

260
00:17:31,640 --> 00:17:33,530
Helping him find his way, right?

261
00:17:33,530 --> 00:17:38,280
Were you helping him on the overpass the other day as well?

262
00:17:39,020 --> 00:17:41,670
We are dating! What's wrong with that?

263
00:17:41,670 --> 00:17:45,000
Mr. Okano, your prejudice is disgusting.

264
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:48,070
Prejudice?

265
00:17:50,050 --> 00:17:53,230
I couldn't help it because I knew nothing of those things.

266
00:17:53,230 --> 00:17:56,090
I don't want you to judge me because of it.

267
00:17:57,330 --> 00:18:01,680
I was just happy to learn from you.

268
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:07,700
Getting advice from you, you were like a senior I never had,

269
00:18:07,700 --> 00:18:09,410
like an older brother.

270
00:18:09,410 --> 00:18:15,060
We... got along fine because I didn't know your sexuality.

271
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:17,510
I mean... In the beginning, you...

272
00:18:17,510 --> 00:18:21,890
I haven't changed since the day I met you.

273
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:27,750
I wanted you to know that. Bye, then.

274
00:18:29,200 --> 00:18:31,550
Aoki, sorry for the wait.

275
00:18:31,550 --> 00:18:32,990
Ida!

276
00:18:32,990 --> 00:18:36,480
- You could have waited inside.
- What?

277
00:18:38,270 --> 00:18:40,010
Well...

278
00:18:47,320 --> 00:18:49,130
Is something wrong?

279
00:18:49,130 --> 00:18:52,150
Not really. Let's go inside.

280
00:18:59,290 --> 00:19:01,630
Ida, I said let's go.

281
00:19:04,750 --> 00:19:07,310
Would you like to have ramen with us?

282
00:19:07,310 --> 00:19:09,830
- What?
- Hey!

283
00:19:09,830 --> 00:19:14,760
Aoki, didn't you look forward to eating ramen with Mr. Okano?

284
00:19:14,760 --> 00:19:17,140
Take a hint.

285
00:19:17,140 --> 00:19:20,600
Aoki, Ida...

286
00:19:20,600 --> 00:19:24,290
it'll be my treat. Shall we eat together?

287
00:19:37,290 --> 00:19:38,610
Where are you going?

288
00:19:38,610 --> 00:19:40,040
To wash my hands.

289
00:19:40,040 --> 00:19:42,910
You're so prim and proper.

290
00:19:51,580 --> 00:19:53,270
Listen.

291
00:19:54,750 --> 00:19:56,780
Yes?

292
00:19:56,780 --> 00:20:00,300
To be honest, it's not easy for me

293
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:02,860
to understand this about you.

294
00:20:03,670 --> 00:20:08,720
But... I was wrong to break a promise.

295
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:11,440
I'm sorry.

296
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:14,550
Okay.

297
00:20:15,890 --> 00:20:20,420
By the way, I was really helping that guy find his way before.

298
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:24,980
I'm really sorry for suspecting you were up to something weird.

299
00:20:26,460 --> 00:20:30,870
You know what? You're being way too self-conscious.

300
00:20:30,870 --> 00:20:32,930
You're too quick to jump to conclusions.

301
00:20:32,930 --> 00:20:36,370
I couldn't help it! I may not look it, but I'm pretty popular, you know.

302
00:20:36,370 --> 00:20:39,650
Are you sure? Even a biased jerk like you?

303
00:20:39,650 --> 00:20:43,430
Jeez, don't call me that.

304
00:20:47,380 --> 00:20:51,660
I didn't pick a random guy to date.

305
00:20:54,070 --> 00:20:55,900
I like Ida.

306
00:21:01,120 --> 00:21:02,930
Fair enough.

307
00:21:04,250 --> 00:21:05,590
What are you guys talking about?

308
00:21:05,590 --> 00:21:07,800
Nothing in particular.

309
00:21:07,800 --> 00:21:11,740
- Thank you for waiting. Here is your miso flavored.
- Thanks.

310
00:21:11,740 --> 00:21:14,390
- Here is your salt flavored.
- Good.

311
00:21:14,390 --> 00:21:17,650
- And soy sauce flavored.
- Mine.

312
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:22,320
It looks so good.

313
00:21:23,090 --> 00:21:25,050
We all picked different flavors.

314
00:21:25,050 --> 00:21:27,170
The miso flavor is really good here.

315
00:21:27,170 --> 00:21:29,660
But soy sauce ramen is my favorite of all.

316
00:21:29,660 --> 00:21:32,370
Refreshing salt-flavored one is the best.

317
00:21:32,370 --> 00:21:35,200
- Let's eat!
- Let's dig in.

318
00:21:38,370 --> 00:21:41,300
Wow, it's delicious.

319
00:21:41,310 --> 00:21:43,510
It's so good.

320
00:21:44,790 --> 00:21:47,010
Oh well...

321
00:21:47,010 --> 00:21:51,060
people are free to like whatever they like, I suppose.

322
00:21:51,060 --> 00:21:54,260
♫ While I feel my heart ♫

323
00:21:54,260 --> 00:21:57,200
♫ Leap with excitement, ♫

324
00:21:57,200 --> 00:22:00,240
Oh, it's delicious!

325
00:22:01,810 --> 00:22:03,660
Excuse me.

326
00:22:03,660 --> 00:22:06,940
Could I have some gyoza, beer, and...

327
00:22:06,940 --> 00:22:09,650
- two oolong teas?
- You got it.
(T/N: Oolong Tea - made from the same plant used in black and green teas, but the leaves are processed differently)

328
00:22:11,840 --> 00:22:14,900
I'm sorry, Aoki!

329
00:22:14,900 --> 00:22:17,700
Mr. Okano, you had too much to drink.

330
00:22:17,700 --> 00:22:20,630
- Sorry, Ida.
- It's fine.

331
00:22:21,750 --> 00:22:24,770
And thank you.

332
00:22:26,090 --> 00:22:31,080
It made me happy when you said you'd go talk to Mr. Okano.

333
00:22:31,090 --> 00:22:32,630
Really?

334
00:22:34,170 --> 00:22:37,900
But what should we do with him?

335
00:22:37,900 --> 00:22:41,930
Let's see... should we just leave him here?

336
00:22:41,930 --> 00:22:45,070
Ida, you're heartless.

337
00:22:45,070 --> 00:22:47,080
It was a joke.

338
00:22:47,080 --> 00:22:49,740
I was a little ticked off, too.

339
00:22:49,740 --> 00:22:51,110
What?

340
00:22:55,100 --> 00:22:57,750
Wh-What was that?

341
00:22:57,750 --> 00:23:02,190
Nothing. I was just thinking about how kind you are.

342
00:23:05,300 --> 00:23:09,280
Really? I'm not kind.

343
00:23:09,280 --> 00:23:13,920
Ida always stars at me like that.

344
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:17,950
He's getting heavy. Maybe I should leave him in a random place.

345
00:23:17,950 --> 00:23:20,590
[This drama is a work of fiction]

346
00:23:20,590 --> 00:23:22,790
Should we go somewhere together?
[Next Episode]
[The wished-for first date!]

347
00:23:22,790 --> 00:23:25,310
When you give a cake to the person you like,
your love will be fulfilled.
[A love-fulfilling winter event draws near]

348
00:23:25,310 --> 00:23:26,900
Is it the same as the way Aoki likes you?

349
00:23:26,900 --> 00:23:28,710
He's never told me he likes me.

350
00:23:28,710 --> 00:23:30,590
You don't want to date me sincerely, do you?

351
00:23:30,590 --> 00:23:36,680
You'll find out everything about their first love on a special episode on December 4th.
